# Uber Report Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project is a Power BI dashboard created to analyze Uber trip data and understand business performance.

## Objective
The objective of this project is to analyze trip details and identify important insights such as bookings, revenue, trip patterns, and customer trends.

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI
- CSV Dataset
- Data Visualization

## Features
- Trip details analysis
- Revenue analysis
- Ride booking trends
- Customer and trip performance insights
- Interactive dashboard visualization

## Files Included
- uber_trip.pbix (Power BI dashboard file)
- Uber Trip Details.csv (Dataset used for analysis)

## Outcome
This dashboard helps in understanding Uber business performance and supports better decision making through data analysis.
